overview: Travel shapes the young. Rachel and Lauren won't tell you otherwise! The two friends like to challenge each other more naughty than the other. Like that of crossing France to join a man met on the internet. But, as usual, they will leave unexpectedly, without a car or money. Which will make the journey all the more exciting for these two chicks, whose incredible assets and level of perversity will allow them to get out of highly explosive situations!
title: The Chosen One
